###########################################################################
#  footnote_multiple - three distinct @FootNote bodies attached to a    #
#  single paragraph, each producing its own bottom-of-page entry.  The  #
#  PostScript and SVG back ends should agree on numbering and on the    #
#  vertical placement of the footnote band.                              #
###########################################################################

@SysInclude { doc }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
Aristotle@FootNote { Greek philosopher, 384-322 BCE. } wrote about
ethics@FootNote { Nicomachean Ethics, c. 340 BCE. } and politics,@FootNote {
Politics, eight books on the polis. } leaving a deep mark on the
medieval scholastic tradition.
@End @Text
